					<description><![CDATA[I looked at so many apps because the piece of paper my trainer gave is a pain in the butt to carry around!  When I read &quot;notebook&quot; something clicked and I made a notebook using Microsoft Onenote for my phone which syncs to my laptop.  It&#039;s pretty much what you do except I don&#039;t have another thing to keep track of and I put reminders in there to go the gym and to track this stuff.  Thanks for the great idea.]]></description>
